  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 14 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 2 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 13</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This relatively obscure technique allows you to feed Chakra into a seal to increase the weight of an object. When performing the technique, you may pour up to 5 Chakra into the seal. The seal radiates a Chakra Signature based on the amount of Chakra in it, and feels identical to your Signature. Each point of Chakra in the seal, increases the object's weight by 5 lbs. You may perform this technique again (without having to draw the seal) to add more Chakra to it, though it may not hold more than 5 Chakra.<br><br>As an instant action, you may make a Chakra Control check (DC 10 + 2 per point of Chakra removed) to reduce the Chakra contained within in the seal by up to 1 per 2 levels.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
